claim.claim-text:
1. A printed circuit board comprising:
a base substrate;
a heating element attached to one surface of the base substrate;
a circuit layer formed on one surface of the base substrate and including a pad part on which the heating element is mounted and an opening formed on one side or both sides of the pad part;
a heat sink attached to another surface of the base substrate; and
a heat radiation coating material applied to the opening to thereby radiate heat of the heating element conducted to the base substrate to outside.
